{"tid":1709782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"城大手足清路障比私家車過，因為有小朋友要去醫院","createTime":"2019-11-12T03:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T03:54:14.000Z","uid":129622,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cfa29256c50c337902ad01b4addda7d3f086cbae","tid":1709782,"uid":129622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"【1015】城大宿舍外的歌和老街，繼續有示威者聚集及堵路，有私家車想駛過，在場人士起初責罵，但被告知車輛需要往醫院及有小朋友在內，馬上一同動手將阻礙物移開，車輛得以掉頭駛離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/993335234392311/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F993335234392311%2F&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYg9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=39bb6d9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/993335234392311/</a><br />\n<br />\n相反班狗係將軍澳連救護車都阻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n司機又好手足又好<br />\n口角不如直接傾下咩事<br />\n有需要大家都會讓步<br />\n唔好打算撞手足 一定走唔甩 架車即刻變路障<br />\n手足亦唔洗一口角就爆玻璃 塞路先係主線"},{"pid":"8c5a074e868004ceb4daf7da3c8940e2d7d60b11","tid":1709782,"uid":31752,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"話去醫院就真係去醫院咩"},{"pid":"5803c07aa97327b73f7469c8155d05eb84d40c51","tid":1709782,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8c5a074e868004ceb4daf7da3c8940e2d7d60b11","tid":1709782,"uid":31752,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"話去醫院就真係去醫院咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"咁你有証據証人講大話？？"},{"pid":"7cd8581a036b5c1a2632988c28496afdf518c371","tid":1709782,"uid":123991,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8c5a074e868004ceb4daf7da3c8940e2d7d60b11","tid":1709782,"uid":31752,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"話去醫院就真係去醫院咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"你老母去醫院就去醫院咩"},{"pid":"c04098202f61ce7ae93b907ab7053ce56ae87ab9","tid":170978